## 3. Verify Execution
1.  Go to the **Actions** tab in your repository.
2.  Select **Daily Crawler** from the left sidebar.
3.  Click **Run workflow** (button on the right) to test it immediately.
4.  Wait for the job to finish and check the logs to see the crawled data.

